      "content": "\"letting go of the struggle\" and \"finding peace in impermanence\"... that sounds a lot like just giving up. if nothing matters and the universe is indifferent, then the struggle is just unnecessary suffering, right? if there's no point in staying, isn't it more logical to just... stop? why keep up the act if the end result is always going to be nothing?",
